    <briefdescription>
<para>A class to indicate that an explicit time stepper should be constructed for use in other operators. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class is a time stepper builder. A time stepper builder is designed to construct a time stepper upon request. This allows the simulation to choose the method without needing to know the specifics of the types with which it should be initialised. This class should be specialised for the explicit time stepper builders. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
